{
  "texts": [
    "It contains all listening records of about 1000 users.",
    "In order to have sequences long enough for statistically relevant fits, only users with more than 1000 logs have been retained.",
    "The final data set contains 890 users having a median number of listened records of 13,985.",
    "Each record contains the timestamp at which a user listened to a given song.",
    "In the database, each song is associated to a title, the artist's name and a unique MusicBrainz Identifier (MBID), which can be used to obtain additional metadata 81."
  ]
}